Partition #2
This is the partition for the intermediate reaction stage. This acts as an intermediate cluster configuration that
  operates as a transfer coupling partition. This is indicated by the -1 NEX value that tells FRESCO that the cross sections 
  for this partition are not printed.
The whole reaction chain is as follows: 58Ni(6Li,a)60Cu(a,d)62Zn.
The Q-value inputted, 9.7796 MeV, corresponds to the first half of the equation: 58Ni(6Li,a)60Cu.

