SECTION 4: OVERLAPS AND SPECTROSCOPIC AMPLITUDES


   ***** 6Li breakup *****
   Overlap of 6Li (projectile, form factor 1), with each and every discretized channel (binned continuum).
   This is the reaction mechanism itself. Below we tell FRESCO "what talks to what?"
   
  1   2   3 3 0 0  5.0     6.0
  
  1       | ICTO   | couple TO partition 1
  2       | ICFROM | couple FROM partition 2

  3       | KIND   | projectile excitation coupling
  3       | IP1    | multipole order Q=3
  0       | IP2    | Coulomb + nuclear coupling
  0       | IP3    | include all reorientation terms

  5.0     | P1     | fragment-target potential KP index
  6.0     | P2     | core-target potential KP index

  This coupling is saying: "use the projectile excitation machinery to couple partition 2 into partition 1."
  i.e. using a multipole coupling, couple the following:
    α+60Cu ↔ 6Li+58Ni

